Data pulled from a MCU of a salvaged Model 3. VIN is encoded in the HRL files.

## HRL Format

The HRL file format seems to consist of blocks of length 0x4000 bytes. It appears each block starts with byte 0x40 and followed by an icreasing number (four bytes). The next four bytes are mostly 0xffffffff.

Here are the block begins:
